               <p>MR. CARR. This is the chisel I found on the ledge where the chest had been standing.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290409-322-person3022">
                  JOHN 
                  LEWIS
               <interp inst="t18290409-322-person3022" type="surname" value="LEWIS"></interp>
